---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Arrivly — Everything you need when you arrive in Australia"
  description="Compare SIM cards, health insurance, bank accounts and money transfer — built for international students in Australia. No ads, no bias."
  ogTitle="Arrivly — Everything international students need in Australia"
  ogDescription="The first weeks in Australia are overwhelming. We make the easy stuff easy.">

  <!-- ── Hero ── -->
  <section class="px-6 sm:px-10 pt-12 pb-16 sm:pt-24 sm:pb-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink leading-[1.04] max-w-4xl">
        The first weeks in Australia <br class="hidden sm:block" />
        are overwhelming. <br />
        We make the easy stuff
        <span class="relative inline-block">
          easy.
          <span class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 right-0 h-3 bg-accent -z-10 rounded"></span>
        </span>
      </h1>

      <div class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-muted mt-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed space-y-5">
        <p>When we arrived, we spent weeks on the wrong SIM card, paid too much for health insurance, and didn't know which bank account actually worked for sending money home.</p>
        <p>We built Arrivly so you don't have to figure it out the hard way.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/sim-cards"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-ink text-paper px-7 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-ink/85 transition-colors">
          Compare SIM cards <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#tools"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-ink border border-black/10 hover:bg-warm transition-colors">
          See all tools
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Tools grid ── -->
  <section id="tools" class="px-6 sm:px-10 pb-16 sm:pb-32">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-muted mb-4">What we've figured out for you</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink mb-12 max-w-2xl leading-[1.1]">
        Start here. These four things matter most in your first week.
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

        <a href="/sim-cards"
          class="group bg-warm rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-black/5 hover:border-black/20 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-12 sm:mb-16">
            <span class="text-4xl">📱</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent text-ink">
              Available now
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink mb-2">
            SIM cards
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Most students get this wrong. We tested every major plan — including which ones actually include Nepal, India, and Philippines calls.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
            Compare plans <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/health-insurance"
          class="group bg-warm rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-black/5 hover:border-black/20 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-12 sm:mb-16">
            <span class="text-4xl">🏥</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent text-ink">
              Available now
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink mb-2">
            Health insurance
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Your visa requires it. But most students pay more than they need to. We'll show you the difference.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-ink group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
            Compare providers <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <div class="bg-warm rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-black/5">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-12 sm:mb-16">
            <span class="text-4xl opacity-60">🏦</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/10 text-muted">
              Coming soon
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink mb-2">
            Banking &amp; Credit
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Open your first Australian bank account, then build your credit history when you're ready. We cover every stage — from first account to first credit card.
          </p>
          <span class="text-sm text-faint">In development</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-warm rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-black/5">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-12 sm:mb-16">
            <span class="text-4xl opacity-60">💸</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-black/10 text-muted">
              Coming soon
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light tracking-tight text-ink mb-2">
            Money transfer
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Sending $500 home can cost $5 or $25 depending on who you use. We show you exactly who charges what.
          </p>
          <span class="text-sm text-faint">In development</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Trust strip ── -->
  <section class="px-6 sm:px-10 py-16 sm:py-24 border-t border-black/5">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-10 sm:gap-12">
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-ink mb-3 tracking-tight leading-[1.15]">
          Free to use.<br />Always.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Arrivly is free for students. No paywalls, no sign-ups, no catch. Use it as often as you need — from the week you arrive to the year you graduate.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-ink mb-3 tracking-tight leading-[1.15]">
          We check. Then we<br />show our work.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Every plan shows the date we last verified it and where we got the data. If something is uncertain, we say so. No bluffing.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-light text-ink mb-3 tracking-tight leading-[1.15]">
          Made by someone who<br />went through it too.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          We navigated the Australian student and visa system ourselves. This is the resource we needed and couldn't find.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
